\subtree{
\title{Implementation Workflow}
\p{To add settings to a plugin:}

\ol{
\li{Design settings schema (which fields, types, defaults)}
\li{Create template file in plugin documentation}
\li{Add gitignore entry for \code{\startverb .claude/*.local.md\stopverb}}
\li{Implement settings parsing in hooks/commands}
\li{Use quick-exit pattern (check file exists, check enabled field)}
\li{Document settings in plugin README with template}
\li{Remind users that changes require Claude Code restart}
}

\p{Focus on keeping settings simple and providing good defaults when settings file doesn't exist.}
}
}